Package: MMCoxCL
Type: Package
Title: Function for fitting the Cox model to clustered interval-censored data using a novel minorize-maximiz algorithm
Version: 1.0
Date: 2022-09-03
Author: Tong Wang, Kejun He,  Samiran Sinha
Maintainer: Tong Wang <wangtong@nankai.edu.cn>
Description: parameter estimation and confidence interval calculation for the Cox model with clustered interval-censored data. The code can also handle the non-clustered data scenario. This package contains two functions, Cox_est and SIM_DATA. Cox_est is used for analyzing data using the methodology proposed in Wang et al. SIM_DATA is used for simulating clustered/nonclustered current status data using the Cox model.
License: Unlimited
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.4.6),gaussquad,extraDistr,fda,splines2,nleqslv,numDeriv
Depends: gaussquad
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
